What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Esterquats Market?



Market Analysis and Size

The increasing focus of developed countries towards improving the effectiveness of laundry operations is leading to an increase in the demand for detergent powders and fabric softeners, thus stimulating the demand and supply of ester quats. Along with this, the increase in the use of personal and cosmetic products by consumers with increasing per capita income and lifestyle changes are expected to boost market growth rate during the forecast period.

